name: Tetrafab
overview:
The high-volume, low-cost designing and manufacturing of quality, custom-sewn cases is only part of what we do at Tetrafab. We also offer custom logistics and inventory services to help ensure our clients’ manufacturing and delivery processes run smoothly and efficiently.

Tetrafab adds value to our clients’ manufactured products. We design and manufacture thermal-formed foam cases (also known as EVA, thermoform, and formed foam) and custom-sewn soft cases for sensitive medical equipment, test & measurement instruments, and other portable electronics. Our on-site quality control department employs the most stringent testing to ensure a quality, zero-defect product befitting of our clients’ products and end-users. And, since all of our design and vertically integrated manufacturing are done in-house, we remain highly price-competitive.
